data.description:
Welcome to your dream coastal oasis! This stunning 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is a true gem, offering a lifestyle of luxury, relaxation, and coastal charm. Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, just a short walk from both the beach and the river, this beautifully updated and meticulously maintained property is the perfect place to call home.As you approach this picturesque residence, you'll be greeted by its impeccable curb appeal. Let the manicured lawn set the stage for the beauty that lies within. The home's exterior exudes a timeless elegance, with a tasteful Bold blend of coastal colors and classic architecture.Now, let's talk about the backyard paradise. Step outside to your own private oasis, where you'll find an inviting inground pool and a soothing spa. . The spacious deck and patio area provide the ideal space for outdoor entertaining, whether you're hosting a summer BBQ or a poolside cocktail party. Jump it and make a splash.
Don't miss your opportunity to own this coastal paradise. This 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home with an inground pool and spa, cosmetic updates, and a prime location between the beach and river is a rare find. Whether you're looking for a full-time residence or a vacation getaway, this property offers the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and coastal living. Contact us today to schedule a private tour and experience the magic of this exceptional home for yourself. Your dream home by the beach awaits
